---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import gii_digital_technology_img_4_svg from "../../../public/images/gii_digital_technology_img_4.webp";
import gii_digital_technology_img_5_svg from "../../../public/images/gii_digital_technology_img_5.webp";
import gii_digital_technology_img_6_svg from "../../../public/images/gii_digital_technology_img_6.webp";
import gii_digital_technology_img_7_svg from "../../../public/images/gii_digital_technology_img_7.webp";
---

<section
  class="main-component flex flex-col bg-[#243544]"
  aria-labelledby="digitalStrategyTitle"
>
  <section
    class="main-component flex flex-col bg-[#243544] py-16 lg:py-24"
    aria-labelledby="digitalResponsibilityTitle"
  >
    <div
      aria-label="Digital Responsibility Title Wrapper"
    >
      <div
        class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto"
        aria-label="Digital Responsibility Title  container "
      >
        <h2
          class="w-full self-stretch text-center text-[26px] leading-snug lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-white"
        >
          Le numérique responsable a différents champs d&#x27;action
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="my-16 flex w-full flex-col justify-center py-6 text-white px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-md:px-5 max-md:max-w-full"
      aria-label="Digital Responsibility Introduction"
    >
      <p
        class="w-full gap-2.5 self-stretch max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto text-center text-lg lg:text-xl leading-snug"
      >
        En se focalisant notamment sur la véritable valeur ajoutée des services
        numériques.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="max-md:px-5 max-md:max-w-full px-4 lg:px-8"
      aria-label="Digital Responsibility Main Section"
    >
      <div
        class="mx-auto container"
        aria-label="Digital Responsibility Main  container "
      >
        <div
          class="mx-auto w-full xl:max-w-screen-lg"
          aria-label="Digital Responsibility Grid"
        >
          <div class="block flex-wrap justify-between md:flex">
            <div
              class="px-5 flex mb-6 w-full flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white text-[#283E52] p-4 md:flex md:w-[calc(35%_-_20px)] relative"
              aria-label="GREEN for IT  container "
            >
              <h3 class="text-center text-2xl font-semibold absolute top-4">
                Le GREEN for IT
              </h3>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center py-12">
                <div
                  class="ml-2 flex w-1/2 flex-col items-end justify-center gap-1"
                >
                  <Image
                    alt="Letter R"
                    src={gii_digital_technology_img_4_svg}
                    width="145"
                    height="180"
                    class="md:w-full lg:w-auto"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="h-full ml-2 flex flex-col justify-between gap-1">
                  <p aria-label="Refuse">ÉFUSER</p>
                  <p aria-label="Reduce">ÉDUIRE</p>
                  <p aria-label="Reuse">ÉUTILISER</p>
                  <p aria-label="Repair">ÉPARER</p>
                  <p aria-label="Recycle">ECYCLER</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="px-5 mb-6 flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-12 rounded-2xl text-[#283E52] bg-white p-4 md:w-[calc(65%_-_15px)]"
            >
              <h3 class="text-center text-2xl font-semibold">
                Le IT for GREEN
              </h3>
              <Image
                alt="IT for GREEN"
                src={gii_digital_technology_img_5_svg}
                class="w-full"
              />
            </div>
            <div
              class="lg:mt-4 px-5 lg:px-10 mb-6 flex w-full flex-col items-center rounded-2xl text-[#283E52] bg-white p-4 md:w-[calc(65%_-_15px)]"
            >
              <h3 class="text-center text-2xl font-semibold">
                Le IT for HUMAN
              </h3>
              <div
                class="flex lg:flex-row-reverse items-center lg:gap-16 gap-10 py-12 flex-col"
              >
                <Image
                  alt="IT for HUMAN"
                  src={gii_digital_technology_img_6_svg}
                  width="357"
                  height="314"
                  class=""
                />
                <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
                  <p>
                    Accès à l&#x27;information pour les personnes en situation
                    de handicap
                  </p>
                  <p>Aider à la santé</p>
                  <p>Créer de l&#x27;emploi</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="lg:mt-4 px-5 mb-6 flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-between gap-12 rounded-2xl text-[#283E52] bg-white p-4 md:w-[calc(35%_-_20px)]"
            >
            <h3 class="text-center text-2xl font-semibold">
              Le HUMAN for IT
            </h3>
            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-col">
              <div
                class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between h-full gap-3"
              >
                <p>Droits des êtres humains</p>
                <p>Conditions de travail</p>
                <p>Droits du travail</p>
                <p>Impacts sociaux</p>
              </div>
            </div>
              <Image
                alt="HUMAN for IT"
                src={gii_digital_technology_img_7_svg}
                width="260"
                height="171"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mx-auto lg:px-0 px-4 max-md:max-w-full lg:w-auto flex min-h-[50px] w-full flex-col items-center justify-center text-xl font-semibold leading-snug text-lime-500"
      aria-label="Learn More Section"
    >
    <div class="mx-auto text-center w-full lg:w-auto mt-16">
      <a
        href="https://drive.digitalforest.fr/apps/calendar/appointment/swJexzmM8c8t"
        class="bg-[#AEC90B] px-12 py-2 container font-semibold text-slate-800 rounded-md hover:bg-[#AEC90B] transition inline-block"
        aria-label="Book a demo"
      >
      Réserver une démo
      </a>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="bg-white" aria-label="Digital Strategy Wrapper">
    <div
      class="max-xl:px-4 flex flex-col py-16 lg:py-24"
      aria-label="Digital Strategy container"
    >
      <div class="container mx-auto text-[#243544] flex flex-col">
        <h2
          class="w-full self-stretch text-left text-[26px] leading-snug lg:text-4xl font-semibold"
          aria-label="Digital Strategy Title"
        >
          Déployer une stratégie Numérique Responsable
        </h2>
        <div
          class="mt-16 flex flex-col w-full justify-center gap-10 rounded-2xl bg-[#243544] lg:p-10 p-5 text-xl leading-10"
          aria-label="Digital Strategy Content Wrapper"
        >
          <p
            class="text-white text-lg lg:text-xl w-full !leading-[2]"
            aria-label="Digital Strategy Intro Text"
          >
            Déployer une stratégie Numérique Responsable pour les entreprises et
            les collectivités est un projet collaboratif, à la fois progressif
            et progressiste.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="mt-16 flex flex-col w-full items-starts gap-10 text-lg lg:text-xl leading-10"
          aria-label="Digital Strategy Sub Content Wrapper"
        >
          <p
            class="text-start text-lg lg:text-xl"
            aria-label="Digital Strategy Sub Text 1"
          >
            Avec la méthodologie Green IT Impact de <a
              href="https://green-web.fr"
              class="underline inline-block">Green WEB</a
            >, concepteur de l'IT for ReGen (la technologie au service de la
            régénération du vivant), nos experts vous accompagnent du diagnostic
            jusqu'à l'obtention de résultats concrets (ou remboursés).
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-lg lg:text-xl"
            aria-label="Digital Strategy Sub Text 2"
          >
            Oui, nous nous engageons sur les résultats obtenus !
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto text-center w-full lg:w-auto mt-16">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-[#AEC90B] px-12 py-2 container font-semibold text-slate-800 rounded-md hover:bg-[#AEC90B] transition inline-block"
            aria-label="Book a demo"
          >
            Contactez-nous
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
